title: NEWS: Gil-galad & Celebrimbor Reveals, Philippa Boyens & Miranda Otto Return to Rohan!
description:
This week, we're talking with guests Men of the West and The Clueless Fangirl about the articles on Gil-galad and Celebrimbor in The Rings of Power, Philippa Boyens' interview on War of the Rohirrim, and Miranda Otto's return to Middle-earth as Éowyn!

Philippa Boyens interview: https://www.theonering.net/torwp/2022/06/28/113412-exclusive-philippa-boyens-talks-the-war-of-the-rohrrim-with-theonering-net/

Celebrimbor article: https://www.fandom.com/articles/rings-of-power-elf-celebrimbor

Gil-galad article: https://nerdist.com/article/lord-of-the-rings-the-rings-of-power-who-is-gil-galad-benjamin-walker-interview-exclusive-images/
